    "sections": {
        "description": "<p>Freesoul Switch Themes allows you to load multiple themes on the same WordPress website.<\/p>\n<p>You can assign a different theme in a permanent way, or just see a preview of a specific page or post with a different theme.<\/p>\n<p>You will find a section on the edit page screen.<\/p>\n<p>Having a theme preview while the website is public is useful when you are trying to understand if the actual theme is causing an issue on the front-end.<\/p>\n<p>Assigning a different theme on specific pages may be useful when you want a different style only on some pages.<\/p>\n<p>The actual version supports only the front-end and no custom post types.<\/p>\n",
        "installation": "<ol>\n<li>Upload the entire <code>freesoul-switch-theme<\/code> folder to the <code>\/wp-content\/plugins\/<\/code> directory.<\/li>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the &#8216;Plugins&#8217; menu in WordPress.<\/li>\n<li>You will find the plugin options in each single page and post and a global settings page under the plugins admin menu<\/li>\n<li>All done. Good job!<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>1.0.7<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: missing valid plugin header<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.6<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: possibility to add custom URLs in wp-config.php<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.5<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: Post meta not deleted after plugin deletion<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.4<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: PHP warning if the user has no file writing rights during deactivation<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.3<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: PHP warning if the user has no file writing rights<\/li>\n<li>Fix: child themes not loading<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.2<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: solved page link update issue<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.1<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: translation in Italian<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial Release<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n",
        "screenshots": "<ol><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/freesoul-switch-theme\/assets\/screenshot-1.png?rev=1901975\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/freesoul-switch-theme\/assets\/screenshot-1.png?rev=1901975\" alt=\"Settings in each single page and post\"><\/a><p>Settings in each single page and post<\/p><\/li><\/ol>",
        "reviews": "<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Simple and easy to use<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/cotajp\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/fcb98c09c21d4ae3c31f47e73c12bb80?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/fcb98c09c21d4ae3c31f47e73c12bb80?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/cotajp\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">COTA <small>(cota.jp)<\/small><\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">January 30, 2024<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">It is used to switch themes on a permanent, page-by-page basis. Other similar plugins were unstable, but this plugin is stable. I hope it will be available for a long time.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Genius plugin!<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/vovastik\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/8b00e4d44270fa43ed0446e184f34435?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/8b00e4d44270fa43ed0446e184f34435?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/vovastik\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Vladimir Bender <small>(Vovastik)<\/small><\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">July 18, 2022<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">As they say, everything ingenious is simple.\nThis is a real salvation from a ton of problems with one click.\nIf some plugin you need uses Bootstrap (like Classified Listing by RadiusTheme) and conflicts with your theme, The Freesoul Switch Theme plugin will help you.\nDo you really need a network?\nIf all you want is for different collections of web pages to look very different, then you can probably achieve what you want in a single site by using a plugin to switch themes, templates, or stylesheets \u2014 Freesoul Switch Theme plugin.\nWe are looking forward to the release of PRO for switching themes for custom pages.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great plugin<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/ellaod\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/8453b1d829a7620dde4b35d69c17cfff?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/8453b1d829a7620dde4b35d69c17cfff?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/ellaod\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">ellaod<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 14, 2020<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">Really useful and great plugin, simple and easy to use, does exactly what it says and works perfectly.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Amazing!<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org